Sure, here are some example sentences using the Serbian word "cigaretu" in different forms and positions:

1. *Cigaretu* sam upalio pre nego što sam izašao iz kuće. (I lit up a cigarette before leaving the house.)
2. Da li imaš neku *cigaretu* za mene? (Do you have a cigarette for me?)
3. Moram da kupim nove *cigarete*. (I need to buy new cigarettes.)
4. *Cigaretom* sam pokušavao da se opustim. (I was trying to relax with a cigarette.)
5. Uvek imam *cigarete* kod sebe. (I always have cigarettes with me.)
6. Zbog pušenja *cigareta*, moje zdravlje je ugroženo. (Smoking cigarettes has endangered my health.)
7. Ne želim da vidim *cigaretu* u tvojim rukama. (I don't want to see a cigarette in your hands.)
8. Našao sam jednu polovnu *cigaretu* u pepeljari. (I found a used cigarette in the ashtray.)

I hope these sentences help you understand how to use the word "cigaretu" in different forms and positions.